{"tid":1692235,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 蒙面法公聽會爭凳仔 今撳爆F5搶攻 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T09:15:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"429c659fb4ba133a226cf0eeb4276c07ac9f8477","tid":1692235,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/I3OWB4BQM4ZW3F54IDO3ZCR43I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FI3OWB4BQM4ZW3F54IDO3ZCR43I%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfp1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=4ecd6597\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FI3OWB4BQM4ZW3F54IDO3ZCR43I%2F&h=314502a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/I3OWB4BQM4ZW3F54IDO3ZCR43I/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n蒙面法公聽會爭凳仔 今撳爆F5搶攻 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191104/large/1572799201_a413.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191104%2Flarge%2F1572799201_a413.jpg&h=c71b241f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nauthor<br />\n專欄作家 : 李八方<br />\n<br />\n實施咗近一個月嘅《禁止蒙面規例》，到底有乜用？根本係製造白色恐怖，好似萬聖節前夕咁吖，市民連化個靚妝落街過節都提心吊膽，試問呢個香港點會仲係以前咁自由吖！雖然特首林鄭月娥拒聽民意，但呢條以「先訂立後審議」形式推行嘅惡法，喺民主派爭取下都有得舉行公聽會，但由於名額有限，慎防建制派又壟斷，民主派呼籲大家今朝早齊齊做鍵盤戰士，不停狂按F5掣登記報名。一旦市民成功登記，唔知畀唔畀蒙面出席聽證會呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免變建制派一言堂<br />\n<br />\n建制派早前喺立法會《禁止蒙面規例》小組委員會，分別派出以開會嗰陣瞓覺出名嘅民建聯黃定光，以及準備生第二胎、腹大便便嘅新民黨容海恩，成功搶佔該委員會正、副主席職位後，民主派一直要求開聽證會畀市民發表意見。最終小組決定喺本周六舉行公聽會，但當日只限150個名額，仲要係先到先得。<br />\n<br />\n唔少民主派有見及此，呼籲市民記住踴躍報名表態，好似新同盟范國威咁，佢噚日特別喺IG出post，呼籲大家今朝9點去到立會呢個連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/Invite.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp3.legco.gov.hk%2Fors%2Fchinese%2FInvite.aspx&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfp1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=92173b08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/Invite.aspx</a> ，準時喺電腦按F5掣，要搶喺最早嘅時間登記報名，以免公聽會變成建制派團體等人「一言堂」。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨譚文豪都叫大家要搶攻，唔好畀建制派成員攞晒嘅發言機會，以免製造好多人支持蒙面法假象，特別呼籲和理非一族上場保護香港人，希望反映真實意見後，更多國際傳媒報道香港真相！"},{"pid":"342db7c6484a966809c2dc3784333ec9b9d433cd","tid":1692235,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"今朝9點。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f057e4a235b3c00b77f832ff3bafb8b97309b8e6","tid":1692235,"uid":60408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"342db7c6484a966809c2dc3784333ec9b9d433cd","tid":1692235,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"今朝9點。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:37:27.000Z","msg":"宜家先講.."},{"pid":"447964ba70c305648040e776d5e70398f23b3530","tid":1692235,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aaee6f56699e759e4dd5e17d20e14d270998e3d","tid":1692235,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429c659fb4ba133a226cf0eeb4276c07ac9f8477","tid":1692235,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/I3OWB4BQM4ZW3F54IDO3ZCR43I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FI3OWB4BQM4ZW3F54IDO3ZCR43I%